{"arkId":"cl010091967","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010091967","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Le Tibre","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Le Tibre"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1688 - 1690","currentLocation":"[SCULPT] Jardin des Tuileries","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1688,"endYear":1690,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Bourdict, Pierre","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q18147621"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MR 1765","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"Sculptures des jardins","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"groupe","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; P. Bourdict MDCXC (sur le rocher au-dessous de la corne d\u0027abondance)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,62","displayDimension":"1,62 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,17","displayDimension":"3,17 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"1,32","displayDimension":"1,32 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"marbre","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Copie du Tibre du Vatican, ex\u00e9cut\u00e9e lors du s\u00e9jour du sculpteur \u00e0 l\u0027Acad\u00e9mie de France \u00e0 Rome (1685-1690). Commenc\u00e9 un an apr\u00e8s le Nil de Lorenzo Ottoni, auquel il devait faire pendant, le marbre fut termin\u00e9 en m\u00eame temps, selon une lettre du directeur de l\u0027Acad\u00e9mie, La Teuli\u00e8re, le 9 mars 1688. L\u0027\u0153uvre fut mise en caisse \u00e0 Rome, o\u00f9 elle est attest\u00e9e ainsi en 1709. Elle quitta Rome en avril 1715, quand le directeur de l\u0027Acad\u00e9mie organisa le transport des grands marbres de son \u00e9tablissement. L\u0027ensemble arriva \u00e0 Marly en ao\u00fbt 1715, et les fleuves furent plac\u00e9s dans le parc. Le Tibre est plac\u00e9 aux Tuileries avec son pendant le Nil, au pourtour du bassin octogonal, en mars 1719. Le Tibre du Vatican est conserv\u00e9 au mus\u00e9e du Louvre, d\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"material":[{"value":"marbre"}],"objectType":[{"value":"groupe"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Bresc-Bautier, Genevi\u00e8ve, La sculpture des jardins de Marly, Paris, Louvre \u00e9ditions, 2019","bibliographyDate":"2019","bibliographyDetail":"p. 136-139, n\u00b0 18","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Milovanovic, Nicolas ; Maral, Alexandre (dir.), Versailles et l\u0027Antique, cat. exp. (Versailles, Mus\u00e9e national des ch\u00e2teaux de Versailles et de Trianon, du 13 novembre 2012 au 17 mars 2013), Paris, Artlys, 2012","bibliographyDate":"2012","bibliographyDetail":"p. 256","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Bresc-Bautier, Genevi\u00e8ve ; Pingeot, Anne, Sculptures des jardins du Louvre, du Carrousel et des Tuileries, 2, Paris, 1986","bibliographyDate":"1986","bibliographyDetail":"t. II, 49, n\u00b0 45","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[{"o